This paper is about Machine Reading Comprehension (MRC) for Vietnamese text, which falls under the category of Natural Language Processing (NLP) in Computer Science. The paper discusses the development of a new MRC dataset for Vietnamese, which is a task that involves understanding unstructured text and answering questions about it. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP and related tasks. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these sub-categories also cover topics related to NLP and machine learning.
